	Renamed the base package QScintilla2. Platform portability fixes
	from Ulli. The qsci data directory is now installed (where API files
	will be kept).
	[2a61d65842fb]

2006-10-13  phil  <phil>

	* Python/sip/qsciscintilla.sip, qt/qscintilla.pro,
